# YORKU

IMAPAccount yorku
Host mypost.yorku.ca
User "ifruend"
PassCmd "lpass show --password 5564893240753051762"
UseIMAPS yes

IMAPStore yorku-remote
Account yorku
UseNameSpace yes
Path INBOX

MaildirStore yorku-local
Path ~/mail/yorku/
Inbox ~/mail/yorku/INBOX/
SubFolders Legacy

Channel yorku
Master :yorku-remote:
Slave :yorku-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
SyncState *

